title: SPY + JOHN JOHN FLORENCE
description: It's been nearly a decade since John John Florence joined the SPY family, and he has since grown from a grom phenom to the clear leader of the new guard. Like the classic punk and metal music that fill his head space, he's applying technical mastery, speed, distortion and heavy amplification to an expanding catalog of new school tricks.
